{"id":18963,"date":"2014-05-03T18:49:11","date_gmt":"2014-05-03T14:49:11","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=18963"},"modified":"2023-08-28T19:47:04","modified_gmt":"2023-08-28T15:47:04","slug":"jahiliyyah-stop-acting-on-quran","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/03\/jahiliyyah-stop-acting-on-quran\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Ignorance: Knowledge gone if people stop applying Quran"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Ziyad ibn Labid reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>There will be a time when knowledge disappears<\/strong>.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, how can knowledge disappear when we read the Quran and we will teach it to our children until the Day of Resurrection?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>May your mother be bereft of you, Ziyad! I thought you were the wisest man in Medina. Do not these Jews and Christians read the Torah and the Gospel, but they do not act upon what is in them<\/strong>?\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4048<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Ibn Kathir<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0632\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0644\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0634\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0626\u064b\u0627 \u0630\u064e\u0627\u0643\u064e \u0639\u0650\u0646\u0652\u062f\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0630\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u00a0\u0642\u064f\u0644\u0652\u062a\u064f \u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u06